It is currently 3 AM on Sunday, February 16 and I was just woken up from my sleep by loud gushing water leaking from my ceiling through some cracks in my doorframe between my bedroom and my bathroom. I don't know. Right now, I am using an empty trashcan to collect the water in case this happens again while I am sleeping.
